title: Lunchbox vs. Ladies: NFL Trivia Championship! + Bobby Asks Kenny Chesney A Cheesy Question + Should Eddie Get A Harley Davidson?
itunes:title: Lunchbox vs. Ladies: NFL Trivia Championship! + Bobby Asks Kenny Chesney A Cheesy Question + Should Eddie Get A Harley Davidson?
description:
Lunchbox takes on listener Jamie in another round of "Lunchbox vs Ladies: NFL Trivia". Last week's match ended in a tie. This will be the final match of the season to see if a lady can FINALLY prove Lunchbox wrong and beat him at his own game! Bobby talks with Kenny Chesney about which of his #1 songs he likes performing the least, when he first became known as ‘Island Kenny’ and then hits him with a very cheesy question. Plus, we debate whether or not Eddie is a Harley Davidson guy!
